|-
| [[File:Whipped_Dream.png|20px]] [[Whipped Dream]] || 50 [[File:Green_Shard_Updated.png|20px]] [[Green Shard|Green Shards]] <br> 75 [[File:Pink_Shard_Updated.png|20px]] Pink Shards || 625 {{Questpoints}}
|}

For details as to where one can purchase these items, please check the [[Shard Trader]] page for more information.

==Acquisition==
Pink Shards can be found in the [[Underground]], traded for with the [[Berry Master|Hoenn Berry Master]], and as Loot in [[Dungeons]].

